abstract: 'Dawn of the Jedi' is set a really long time ago.
snippet: 'Dawn of the Jedi' is set a really long time ago.
lead_paragraph: When moviegoers were first introduced to "Star Wars" in 1977 they were promised a story that took place a long time ago, in a galaxy far, far away. At the New York Comic Con on Friday, Dark Horse is revealing a new comic book series, "Dawn of the Jedi," that explores the Jedi myth long before Luke Skywalker took his first step.

headline.main: Picture This: New 'Star Wars' Comics, and Graphic Novels of Stieg Larsson's Trilogy
